  "quest.67D1E0D81B2C5D8D.quest_desc": {
    "original": "The &dLeviathan&r can be found within the &bWater Orb&r structure.\n\nThis is found scattered throughout the &bOcean&r ring.\n\n&eNote&r: You will need an &dAbyssal Sacrifice&r to activate the altar. The items required to craft it can be acquired from the &9Coralssus&r &aGateway of Eternity&r.",
